            <specific name="Languages" > Common, Elven </specific>
            <specific name="Skill Bonuses" > +2 Arcana, +2 History </specific>
            <specific name="Short Description" > Hailing from the Feywild, a realm of verdant magic, the eladrin are masters of arcane power. </specific>
